fields.name: Core Team 1
fields.description: Core Services form the backbone of the company’s technological infrastructure, ensuring security, accessibility, and efficient communication between all other services. These include authentication, user management, notifications, and monitoring, allowing the entire ecosystem to function in an integrated and secure manner.

These include authentication, user management, notifications, and monitoring, allowing the entire ecosystem to function in an integrated and secure manner.

fields.name: Credit Team
fields.description: Credit Services are responsible for processing and managing credit-related operations, including loan issuance, credit analysis, and payment management. These services enable customers to apply for credit, track their financial obligations, and maintain an up-to-date transaction history.

fields.name: Investiment Team
fields.description: Investment Services provide customers with a platform to invest in various assets, such as stocks, funds, and cryptocurrencies. They include portfolio management, order execution, risk analysis, and access to real-time market data, helping users make informed investment decisions.

fields.name: Wallet Team
fields.description: Wallet Services allow users to store, move, and manage their money digitally. They include features such as balance top-ups, payments, transfers, and withdrawals. These services are essential for providing a seamless and secure experience for everyday financial transactions.
